snippet.title: Best VGM 871 - Advance Wars DS - That's a Wrap! (Credits)
snippet.description:
See also:
Best VGM 1613 - http://youtu.be/N-T8KwCCNh8

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

Nintendo DS
Advance Wars DS (2005)
That's a Wrap! (Credits)
Yoshito Hirano
